Christian Tyrrell, 22, was arrested Wednesday on capital murder charges in connection to the death of 2-year-old Adrian Langlais . 
  John Winkler and Laura Martinez considered themselves Adrian's grandparents . 
  They started noticing bruises and other injuries on the boy in November when his mother started dating Tyrrell . 
  They reported the injuries to Child Protective Services but the agency closed the case in February . 
  Adrian died on March 19 from head trauma . 
  Tyrrell is the son of his girlfriend Jessica Langla is . 
 